results.name: Sublattices of index n in generic 7-dimensional lattice.
reference: M. Baake, "Solution of coincidence problem...", in R. V. Moody, ed., Math. of Long-Range Aperiodic Order, Kluwer 1997, pp. 9-44.
link: Amiram Eldar, Table of n, a(n) for n = 1..10000
Index entries for sequences related to sublattices
formula: f(Q, n)=Sum d*f(Q-1, d), d|n; here Q=7.
mathematica: f[p_, e_] := Product[(p^(e + k) - 1)/(p^k - 1), {k, 1, 6}]; a[1] = 1; a[n_] := Times @@ (f @@@ FactorInteger[n]); Array[a, 100] (* _Amiram Eldar_, Aug 29 2019 *)
results.author: _N. J. A. Sloane_.
